What a performance by @pierregasly in qualifying 🤩

Certainly worthy of a Ferrari, right Franz? @alphataurif1 😉

#F1 #Formula1 #HungarianGP #AlphaTauri #PierreGasly

Tactics, team-work and last-run drama! 👀🤝😳

Qualifying certainly had a spicy finish, with time unfortunately running out for @schecoperez 😅

#F1 #Formula1 #HungarianGP #LewisHamilton #MaxVerstappen #SergioPerez
